OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FConcerns over using student
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fteachers as substitute     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fcover                      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Universities have raised significant   
OL,6, concerns about any plan for student    
OL,7, teachers to be used as substitute cover
OL,8, in schools.                            
OL,10,FThat is according to Education Minister
OL,11,FMichelle McIlveen in just-published    
OL,12,Fresponses to questions from two MLAs.  
OL,14,FThe Department of Education (DE) had   
OL,15,Fdiscussed the idea with universities   
OL,16,Fwho train teachers, said Ms McIlveen.  
OL,18,FBut it would not be "reasonable or fair
OL,19,Fto use student teachers to address the 
OL,20,Fcurrent short-term pressure".          
